subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Fredrik Jacobson sank a 31-foot birdie putt on the 18th hole to finish with a seven-under-par 63 and take a one-shot lead over Bryce Molder after three rounds of the Travelers Championship in Cromwell, Conn.
